{"about_the_game":"Where once stood copper monoliths of gears and progress now grows a vicious garden. Entangling the once-booming city in thorns and bringing new and twisted lifeforms with it. <br><br>Copperfields is an adventure/puzzle platformer that tells the story of nature and perseverance. You navigate through a ruined city while trying to survive the hostile environment that isn\u2019t as dormant as it seems.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578740/extras/Copperfields_banner_1_corrected.png?t=1711615214\" />.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578740/extras/3-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1711615214\" />.<br><br>The game features a physics-based movement that makes the gameplay very immersive and exciting. Zip through the levels, solve puzzles, and do cool unnecessary parkour tricks with your one-wheeled robot body!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578740/extras/Copperfields_banner_3_corrected.png?t=1711615214\" />.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578740/extras/2-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1711615214\" />.<br><br>Use your surroundings and remnants of the robot civilization to help yourself go through levels. The tools left by the robots are yours to use and you will need all the help you can get to survive!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578740/extras/Copperfields_Banner_4_corrected.png?t=1711615214\" />.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2578740/extras/8-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1711615214\" />.<br><br>Operate old mechanisms, discover new lifeforms, and find your place in the world! And, if all else fails\u2026<strong>Run</strong>.","background":"https://shared.aka